The '''media repository''' is a directory in SVN where we store the blender files, the original textures/images in gimp/inkscape format, etc.

You may obtain the media repository by obtaining URL
<code>https://svn.code.sf.net/p/supertuxkart/code/media/trunk</code>

Under Unix, the checkout command-line would look like :
<code>svn checkout https://svn.code.sf.net/p/supertuxkart/code/media/trunk stk_media_repo</code>

You can also browse it online [https://sourceforge.net/p/supertuxkart/code/ at sourceforge].
